    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "* **Tìm $q$:** $u_4 = u_1 \\cdot q^3 \\Rightarrow 24 = 3 \\cdot q^3 \\Rightarrow q^3 = 8 \\Rightarrow q = 2$."
